{{reflist}}
{{fake heading|sub=2|References}}
{{refbegin}}
* {{cite book |last=Elk |first=Anne |title=[[Anne Elk's Theory on Brontosauruses]] |date=November 16, 1972}}<!--This is CITEREFElk1972-->
{{refend}}
}}

{{markup|title=Shortened footnotes using {{tl|sfn}}:
